Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11), g++ (>= 7)
Standards-Version: 4.6.0

Package: sista
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight, fast, memory-safe, OS-agnostic library for terminal games
 Sista provides a small C++ library with a C API that helps build terminal
 videogames and animations. It includes terminal ANSI helpers, field and pawn
 primitives, and optional development headers for C/C++ integration.
